<item>
            <title>[LU-1478] 1.8.6.81 client with 2.1.1 server MPIIO file locking issue</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1478</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running a MPI-IO task requiring concurrent read locks fail using 1.8.6 clients on a 2.1.1 server. The issue is not present in 2.1.1 clients.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Easily duplicated by running a test mpi-io job on a 1.8.6 client. I used this benchmark.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://public.lanl.gov/jnunez/benchmarks/mpiiotest.htm&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://public.lanl.gov/jnunez/benchmarks/mpiiotest.htm&lt;/a&gt;  &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment>Clients: Lustre-1.8.6&lt;br/&gt;
Server: Lustre 2.1.1</environment>
        <key id="14740">LU-1478</key>
            <summary>1.8.6.81 client with 2.1.1 server MPIIO file locking issue</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
